opt-viewer 是直接从 LLVM 项目拉过来的
https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/tree/main/llvm/tools/opt-viewer

usage: opt-viewer.py [-h] [--output-dir OUTPUT_DIR] [--jobs JOBS] [--source-dir SOURCE_DIR]
                     [--no-progress-indicator]
                     [--max-hottest-remarks-on-index MAX_HOTTEST_REMARKS_ON_INDEX] [--no-highlight]
                     [--demangler DEMANGLER] [--filter FILTER]
                     yaml_dirs_or_files [yaml_dirs_or_files ...]
